Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家一起去观测天体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.70,0:00:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在寻找彗星时却发现了骸骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭开散乱的香烟之谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.20,0:00:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小孩  头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.10,0:00:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变态观测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.70,0:02:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.90,0:02:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天体观测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.70,0:02:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天体观测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.30,0:02:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  我们这就去看星星吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因为在群马的山里找到了服务还不错的旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.10,0:02:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么要在这么冷的天出来看星星呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天冷才好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.90,0:02:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天冷空气就清澈容易看见星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.50,0:02:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今晚是新月 最适合天体观测了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.90,0:02:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这不是很无聊吗  只是看星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既能学到星座的知识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.20,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且万一发现了什么新的星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.50,0:02:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许还能给它起名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能起名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.80,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要进行多次观测并确认其轨道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.60,0:02:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则发现是无法被承认的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以给小行星起名是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.10,0:03:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是彗星的话  只要找到应该就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.10,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么起名为"米花少年侦探团彗星"怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.60,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用喜欢的名字起名只限于小行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给彗星起名字则要用发现者的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.20,0:03:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申请要早而且最多只能用3个人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.40,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  有时彗星会在世界各地同时被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以会有可能夹杂外国人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3个人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  然后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.60,0:03:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如那颗叫"小林·Berger·Milon"的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.70,0:03:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么发现彗星后赶快完成申请的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.40,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有叫"吉田·圆谷·灰原"的彗星了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 圆谷 灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有加入我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把柯南也加进去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最多只能有3个人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始起一直在干什么呢  柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人不是上次在冲绳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.80,0:04:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害职业棒球手能势的体育记者本山正治先生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.20,0:04:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个案件发生时柯南也在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  稍微有点在意的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点在意的事是指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在调查取证过程中他打了个电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想他是打给谁的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能势选手被杀的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.70,0:04:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经由警方通知其父母和家人了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.20,0:04:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能打给本山自己的熟人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.60,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  要是那个时候问问他本人就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.10,0:04:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是  小森选手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.70,0:04:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和本山 能势是同期入队的棒球选手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们3人经常在停赛期的旅游电视节目中出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去关系似乎不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.10,0:05:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来可能是告之好友死亡的消息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.90,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说4年前引退后他就继承了自家的旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.50,0:05:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是鸟取县的一个叫仓吉的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.80,0:05:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视里曾经介绍过  似乎是家不错的旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.60,0:05:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来和黑衣人似乎没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓吉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.90,0:05:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤  你难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.60,0:05:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星和香烟的暗号（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿笠先生吧  我们已恭候多时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在登记簿上签上你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.20,0:05:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠博士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是被麻雄叫来这里的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  请告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.90,0:06:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟他道歉  他到底在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻雄是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装糊涂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.80,0:06:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是也戴着相同对戒的河野麻雄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.20,0:06:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也收到了他的邀请信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.40,0:06:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  野之宫小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.00,0:06:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我们今天是第一次到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.60,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.30,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.70,0:06:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫野之宫悦子  是我大学的学妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.80,0:06:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她前面提到的河野是我大学的学弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.10,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们有婚约  以前经常来这里住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.00,0:06:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是1年前两人在这里吵了一架后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就一下子不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.10,0:07:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后上周寄来了邀请信叫我们到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她3天前已经等在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他仍然没有现身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.70,0:07:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她从白天就开始喝酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.00,0:07:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她为什么认为素不相识的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.60,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里来也是收到了邀请信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不熟识的我们也是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.40,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个叫河野的家伙那里收到了邀请信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因为我们在1年前的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾和他有一面之缘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请信的内容先不管它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是先来看看罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让我看看那封邀请信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.00,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.40,0:07:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过一年观测的结果 我有了震撼天文界的大发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想听取一下各位的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能否请到天土旅馆来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.90,0:07:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然住宿费由我来承担
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.40,0:08:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果实在无法前来也没办法 不过希望务必来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野麻雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.70,0:08:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从我们等了两天他却踪迹全无这点来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是恶作剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们回去吧  主编
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.10,0:08:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主编
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.20,0:08:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是制作《Space Sunday》天文杂志的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.00,0:08:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位御上先生就是这本杂志的主编
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不仅仅只是主编哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.10,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.00,0:08:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅只是主编是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.50,0:08:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为他发现了新的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给它起了名字  是个很了不起的人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.60,0:08:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里找到的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也教教我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说在哪里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那边  还是这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.60,0:08:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就先到旅馆后面小道的山丘上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.90,0:08:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那边天空会很清澈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是观测星星绝好的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.20,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们愿意的话  还可以借望远镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租金5000日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会赚钱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.60,0:09:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  一定能找到属于我们的星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.30,0:09:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些门外汉  没这么容易找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  主编
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.30,0:09:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你们真是不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.90,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管知识多么丰富  能否发现星星要靠运气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气好的话就能找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 主编
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.60,0:09:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能用你发现星星的运气也帮我找找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那被星星带走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失在宇宙黑暗中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我最重要的那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好远啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.00,0:10:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面说的山丘是那个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说山丘还不如说是悬崖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.90,0:10:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要爬那么高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.90,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.60,0:10:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在日落之前爬上去的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.90,0:10:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经上了年纪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.40,0:10:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时明明叫我们不要把他当老爷爷来对待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就休息10分钟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头  石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们不觉得奇怪吗  刚才的邀请信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.60,0:10:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"如果实在无法前来也没办法"一般会这样写吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.90,0:10:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有无论如何也要把他们叫到这里来的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.20,0:10:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.20,0:11:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骸…骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.00,0:11:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这里会有骸骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.00,0:11:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里也散落了一地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.50,0:11:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下颚骨  上腕骨  大腿骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是从那个悬崖上掉下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.70,0:11:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是很久以前由于事故死亡后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成白骨的某人的遗体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于动物啊 雨水啊 风啊致使它们分散在各处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是被杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是用非常残忍的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  是石灰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.50,0:11:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石灰具有吸收水分后释放热量的性质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.80,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在尸体上及其周围撒上石灰利用下雨时带来的热量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能加快尸体的腐烂速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.80,0:12:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够在短时间内使尸体变为白骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.10,0:12:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就使得死因和死亡时间几乎都推断不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.80,0:12:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非这具白骨就是刚才那些人所说的河野先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.10,0:12:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.90,0:12:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人可是给大家寄去了邀请信的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许就是那个河野先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.10,0:12:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头下面放着戒指和香烟盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指上刻的文字是"ETSUKO to ASAO"(悦子赠于麻雄)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.60,0:12:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是从那个悬崖上被推下来后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人追到这里之前河野先生留下来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.70,0:12:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明自己在这里被杀的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也有可能是犯人故意留下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话犯人应该会让他戴上戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.70,0:12:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意销毁了尸体让别人无法辨认其身份的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.10,0:12:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会特地把这种东西藏在石头下面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能借我一下手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么意思  那个香烟盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的推理是正确的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是装了香烟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是河野先生留下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.30,0:13:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这些香烟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大概是河野麻雄死之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下的有关犯人的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.00,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这不就是六根香烟断了两根而已吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.10,0:13:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两根短香烟上有滤嘴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.30,0:13:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是特地把它弄短放入烟盒的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:14:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果你仔细看藏有香烟盒的石头底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经腐烂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但仍可以看出多余的香烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和当时将香烟弄短的痕迹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.10,0:14:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.90,0:14:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些留在这里的河野先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想让别人看到放在盒子里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.40,0:14:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四根长的和两根短的香烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.80,0:14:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先通知旅馆里的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.10,0:14:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知他们就糟了  先通知警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.60,0:14:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.80,0:14:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在旅馆里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.40,0:14:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是收到河野先生寄的邀请信而聚集在一起的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这具白骨果真是河野先生的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.50,0:14:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄邀请信的就另有其人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.70,0:14:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  被叫来的人都是1年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.90,0:14:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野先生从旅馆消失时也住在这家旅馆里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骸骨被分散的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是风 雨和动物的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是有人故意这么放的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.30,0:15:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄邀请信的人想让谁发现河野先生的白骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是在策划什么阴谋也说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.60,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴谋是指什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.50,0:15:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.60,0:15:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之联络警方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.40,0:15:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点联络他们过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.70,0:15:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这里在信号范围外  连不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.80,0:15:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回旅馆再悄悄给警察打电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.00,0:15:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察吗  发生了什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.40,0:15:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天土先生  你怎么会来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.20,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来这个给望远镜配重的东西忘了放到包里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说这个了  有什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.70,0:15:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  那个配重的东西是指…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.60,0:15:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么奇怪的东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.40,0:15:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.50,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.10,0:16:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 在森林里发现了麻雄的白骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是只有白骨吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.00,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不能确定是麻雄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.10,0:16:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在白骨的旁边有你送给他的刻有名字缩写的对戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是那个叫河野的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.00,0:16:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把谁杀害后特意把戒指放在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.10,0:16:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个戒指放的位置…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个河野先生没有蛀牙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.10,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上颚右侧里面的第二颗臼齿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上颚的臼齿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那些骨头就不是麻雄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的确有蛀牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.20,0:16:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是下面的门牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.70,0:16:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.60,0:16:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发现的遗骸上的治疗痕迹就在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下颚骨的中间啮齿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.40,0:17:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所说 下面的门牙有蛀牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.00,0:17:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他之所以这么说是为了怕你说谎或故意顺着话说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.30,0:17:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才故意说错了蛀牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麻雄  麻雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.70,0:17:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之快点联络警方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.50,0:17:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是电话好像有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.60,0:17:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这个电话怎么只有电源线没有电话线吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.00,0:17:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.30,0:17:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪  刚才明明还用过电话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的电话和备用电话线呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话只有这一部  备用电话线还没买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就联系不到警察了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我开车回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主编
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.40,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.20,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这似乎也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚去外面看了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.30,0:18:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停在这里的汽车的轮胎都被放了气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.50,0:18:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是谁弄松了车子的气门芯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把气放掉让车子就不能用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.10,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把大家留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.60,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道和那个叫河野的家伙有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是杀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.90,0:18:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.80,0:18:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现白骨的时候  你们也看到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.60,0:18:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕上面放着的四根长香烟和两根短香烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.40,0:18:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是死亡讯息吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.00,0:18:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  这才不是死亡讯息呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是麻雄装死 只是让我为难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会恶作剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为麻雄根本不可能死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可爱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之今晚大家一步都不要离开屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.10,0:19:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等天亮了再说比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.20,0:19:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.40,0:19:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香烟有四根长的和两根短的合计六根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.10,0:19:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川先生的话就多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.10,0:19:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天土先生的话又少了1根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.00,0:19:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野之宫小姐和御上先生的话又不能用6根来表示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是片假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川(フタガワ)要14根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天土(アマツチ)要12根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野之宫(ノノミヤ)要8根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.80,0:19:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御上(ミカミ)要9根 都需要这么多的香烟才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不是名字的首字母缩写呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.60,0:20:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.30,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原哀(Haibara Ai)的话H.A正好是6根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.90,0:20:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是犯人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说是举个例子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是举例呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆谷光彦(Tsuburaya Mitsuhiko)的T.M
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉田步美(Yoshida Ayumi)的Y.A也是6根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.60,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说小岛元太是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.20,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们3个人是6根 很浪漫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.20,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我阿笠博士(Agasa Hiroshi)是A.H也是6根哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.30,0:20:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧合啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.00,0:20:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能这个名字首字母缩写是正确答案哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是二川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.00,0:20:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.90,0:20:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果香烟确实代表名字首字母缩写的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.10,0:20:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天土陵司(Amatsuji Ryoji)是A.R
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野之宫悦子(Nonomiya Etsuko)是N.E
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.80,0:21:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御上平八(Migami Heihachi)是M.H
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用6根烟来表示的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有二川肇(Futagawa Hajime)的F.H了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.60,0:21:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在就直接去找那个二川先生的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.10,0:21:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  只是去试探一下而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.60,0:21:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川先生似乎不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.20,0:21:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香烟的滤嘴还是湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从房间出去没有多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.50,0:21:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁在外面走动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是野之宫小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.20,0:21:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是二川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.70,0:21:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连御上先生和天土先生也不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  跟他们说过不要到外面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.30,0:21:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我和光彦还有步美先把野之宫小姐带回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.70,0:21:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士和元太还有灰原去找另外3个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.30,0:21:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.80,0:21:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野之宫小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.40,0:21:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.90,0:21:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.10,0:21:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路是通往发现骸骨的那条路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.60,0:21:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.70,0:22:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是去确认那具白骨是否是河野先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.90,0:22:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.80,0:22:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.80,0:22:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  脖子断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.30,0:22:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.70,0:22:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像握着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.10,0:22:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香烟盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.20,0:22:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是同样的死亡讯息吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.90,0:22:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  这次多了1根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.20,0:24:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不要翻得乱七八糟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔原来带来了望远镜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要找到什么时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.40,0:24:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能成为凶器的是像这伞一样的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.00,0:24:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么剩下来的是天土先生  轮到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.90,0:24:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他一直在看登记簿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.60,0:24:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还仔细看了好几遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.70,0:24:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.50,0:24:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.00,0:24:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星和香烟的暗号（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.70,0:24:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.10,0:24:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字首字母缩写
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.10,0:24:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周是解决篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.30,0:24:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要看我的出色表演哦